#  Production Planning Database Schema and Data

This document contains the core data tables (structure and seeded rows) required for production scheduling and material planning.

---

## 1. PRODUCTS
*Defines all finished goods (SKUs).*

| Column Name | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **product_id** | SKU Identifier (Primary Key) |
| **product_name** | Full product description |
| **category** | Product family (e.g., Shampoo, Skincare) |
| **pack_size** | Retail unit volume |
| **priority** | 1 (Most Critical) to 2 (Standard) |

### Data Rows
| product_id | product_name | category | pack_size | priority |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200 | Citrus Shampoo 200ml | Shampoo | 200ml bottle | **1** |
| CONDITIONER\_HYDRATE\_200 | Hydrating Conditioner 200ml | Conditioner | 200ml bottle | 2 |
| SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | Daily Clean Shampoo 100ml | Shampoo | 100ml bottle | 2 |
| SKINCREAM\_HYDRATE\_100 | Hydration Face Cream 100ml | Skincare | 100ml jar | 2 |

---

## 2. LINES
*Defines the physical production assets.*

| Column Name | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **line_id** | Production Line Identifier (Primary Key) |
| **line_name** | Descriptive name |
| **daily_capacity\_cases** | Max finished cases per day |

### Data Rows
| line_id | line_name | daily\_capacity\_cases |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| LINE\_1 | Line 1 - High Speed Filler | **12000** |
| LINE\_2 | Line 2 - Versatile Filler/Labeler | **10000** |
| LINE\_3 | Line 3 - Multipurpose Line | **8000** |

---

## 3. LINE\_CAPABILITY
*Defines the rate (speed) at which each line can produce each SKU.*

| Column Name | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **line_id** | Reference to LINES |
| **product_id** | Reference to PRODUCTS |
| **rate\_cases\_per\_hour** | Output rate in cases per hour |

### Data Rows
| line_id | product_id | rate\_cases\_per\_hour |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| LINE\_1 | SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200 | **1500** |
| LINE\_2 | SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200 | 1200 |
| LINE\_3 | SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200 | 800 |
| LINE\_1 | CONDITIONER\_HYDRATE\_200 | 1400 |
| LINE\_2 | CONDITIONER\_HYDRATE\_200 | 1100 |
| LINE\_3 | CONDITIONER\_HYDRATE\_200 | 750 |
| LINE\_1 | SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | 1300 |
| LINE\_2 | SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | 1000 |
| LINE\_3 | SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | 700 |
| LINE\_1 | SKINCREAM\_HYDRATE\_100 | 900 |
| LINE\_2 | SKINCREAM\_HYDRATE\_100 | 800 |
| LINE\_3 | SKINCREAM\_HYDRATE\_100 | 600 |

---

## 4. MATERIALS
*Defines all raw materials and packaging components.*

| Column Name | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **material_id** | Component Identifier (Primary Key) |
| **material_name** | Descriptive component name |
| **uom** | Unit of Measure (e.g., kg, bottles, jars) |
| **supplier\_lead\_time\_days** | Time to receive a new order |

### Data Rows
| material_id | material_name | uom | supplier\_lead\_time\_days |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| BASE\_SHAMPOO | Shampoo Base Bulk | kg | 5 |
| BASE\_CONDITIONER | Conditioner Base Bulk | kg | 5 |
| BASE\_SKINCREAM | Face Cream Bulk | kg | **10** |
| FRAGRANCE\_CITRUS | Citrus Fragrance | kg | **14** |
| BOTTLE\_200ML\_CLEAR | 200ml Clear Bottle | bottles | 7 |
| BOTTLE\_100ML\_CLEAR | 100ml Clear Bottle | bottles | 7 |
| JAR\_100ML\_FROST | 100ml Frosted Jar | jars | **10** |
| PUMP\_200ML\_WHITE | 200ml Pump/Cap White | pumps | 7 |
| CAP\_JAR\_100ML | 100ml Jar Lid | lids | 7 |
| LABEL\_200ML | Front/Back Label 200ml | labels | 7 |
| LABEL\_100ML | Front/Back Label 100ml | labels | 7 |
| CARTON\_100ML | Unit Carton 100ml | cartons | 4 |

---

## 5. BILL\_OF\_MATERIALS (BOM)
*Defines the material consumption rate (qty per case) for each product.*

| Column Name | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **product_id** | Reference to PRODUCTS |
| **material_id** | Reference to MATERIALS |
| **qty\_per\_case** | Quantity of material consumed per 1 case of finished product |

### Data Rows (Grouped by Product)

**SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200**
* BASE\_SHAMPOO: **8.0**
* FRAGRANCE\_CITRUS: **0.15**
* BOTTLE\_200ML\_CLEAR: **12.0**
* PUMP\_200ML\_WHITE: **12.0**
* LABEL\_200ML: **24.0**

**CONDITIONER\_HYDRATE\_200**
* BASE\_CONDITIONER: **8.0**
* FRAGRANCE\_CITRUS: **0.10**
* BOTTLE\_200ML\_CLEAR: **12.0**
* PUMP\_200ML\_WHITE: **12.0**
* LABEL\_200ML: **24.0**

**SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100**
* BASE\_SHAMPOO: **9.0**
* FRAGRANCE\_CITRUS: **0.20**
* BOTTLE\_100ML\_CLEAR: **24.0**
* LABEL\_100ML: **48.0**

**SKINCREAM\_HYDRATE\_100**
