* FRAGRANCE\_CITRUS: **0.05**
* JAR\_100ML\_FROST: **24.0**
* CAP\_JAR\_100ML: **24.0**
* LABEL\_100ML: **24.0**
* CARTON\_100ML: **24.0**

---

## 6. INVENTORY\_MATERIALS
*Defines the current stock of all components.*

| Column Name | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **material_id** | Reference to MATERIALS |
| **on\_hand\_qty** | Physical quantity in stock (same UOM as material) |

### Data Rows
| material_id | on\_hand\_qty | UOM |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| BASE\_SHAMPOO | 5000.0 | kg |
| BASE\_CONDITIONER | 2500.0 | kg |
| BASE\_SKINCREAM | 1200.0 | kg |
| FRAGRANCE\_CITRUS | **200.0** | kg |
| BOTTLE\_200ML\_CLEAR | **70000.0** | bottles |
| BOTTLE\_100ML\_CLEAR | 60000.0 | bottles |
| JAR\_100ML\_FROST | 30000.0 | jars |
| PUMP\_200ML\_WHITE | 70000.0 | pumps |
| CAP\_JAR\_100ML | 30000.0 | lids |
| LABEL\_200ML | 140000.0 | labels |
| LABEL\_100ML | 120000.0 | labels |
| CARTON\_100ML | 60000.0 | cartons |

---

## 7. SCHEDULE
*The existing production plan for the week: 2025-10-27 to 2025-10-31.*

| Column Name | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **sched_id** | Unique Schedule ID |
| **line_id** | Reference to LINES |
| **production\_date** | Planned date of production |
| **product_id** | Reference to PRODUCTS |
| **planned\_qty\_cases** | Quantity to be produced |
| **is\_firm** | TRUE (Locked/Promised) / FALSE (Can be bumped) |

### Data Rows
| line_id | production\_date | product_id | planned\_qty\_cases | is\_firm |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **LINE\_1** | 2025-10-27 | SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200 | 8000 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_1 | 2025-10-28 | SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200 | 7500 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_1 | 2025-10-29 | CONDITIONER\_HYDRATE\_200 | 4000 | **FALSE** |
| LINE\_1 | 2025-10-30 | SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200 | 6000 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_1 | 2025-10-31 | SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200 | 4000 | **FALSE** |
| **LINE\_2** | 2025-10-27 | SKINCREAM\_HYDRATE\_100 | 3000 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_2 | 2025-10-28 | SKINCREAM\_HYDRATE\_100 | 3200 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_2 | 2025-10-29 | SKINCREAM\_HYDRATE\_100 | 3500 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_2 | 2025-10-30 | CONDITIONER\_HYDRATE\_200 | 2500 | **FALSE** |
| LINE\_2 | 2025-10-31 | CONDITIONER\_HYDRATE\_200 | 2000 | **FALSE** |
| **LINE\_3** | 2025-10-27 | SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | 3000 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_3 | 2025-10-28 | SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | 3200 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_3 | 2025-10-29 | SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | 3000 | **TRUE** |
| LINE\_3 | 2025-10-30 | SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | 2000 | **FALSE** |
| LINE\_3 | 2025-10-31 | SHAMPOO\_TRAVEL\_100 | 1500 | **FALSE** |

---

## 8. DC\_REQUESTS
*Defines the urgent request that needs planning/action.*

| Column Name | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **request_id** | Unique Request ID |
| **dc_id** | Distribution Center ID |
| **product_id** | Product requested |
| **requested\_qty\_cases** | Quantity requested |
| **requested\_due\_date** | Deadline for the request |
| **promo\_reason** | Context for the request |
| **status** | Current state of the request |

### Data Rows
| dc_id | request\_datetime | product_id | requested\_qty\_cases | requested\_due\_date | promo\_reason | status |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| DC\_EAST | 2025-10-24 09:15:00 | **SHAMPOO\_CITRUS\_200** | **18000 cases** | due **2025-10-30** | "Buy-2-Get-1 Weekend Promo" | **PENDING** |
